    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a G96 6-speed manual transaxle with precise shift gates. The chassis retains its factory-spec multi-link rear suspension and McPherson strut front end, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. Mechanically robust, this example has undergone a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement to ensure long-term drivetrain integrity. While displaying minor aesthetic wear consistent with its mileage, the engine exhibits strong compression and the four-piston monobloc calipers provide firm, fade-resistant deceleration. A driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
