      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche 718 Cayman is the ideal driver\u2019s car for someone who values mechanical integrity and aesthetic cleanliness. Finished in a deep, glossy Agate Grey Metallic, the exterior remains vibrant, having been regularly detailed and garage-kept. While you might find a few minor stone chips on the lower front fascia consistent with careful road use, the body is straight and free of dings. Inside, the black leather interior retains its supportive structure and rich aroma, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every switch, dial, and digital display functions exactly as intended, including the crisp Bose surround sound system. Mechanically, this vehicle is turn-key; it features a full service history with the most recent oil service and brake fluid flush performed just 1,500 miles ago. The Pirelli P Zero tires have ample tread remaining, and the PDK transmission shifts with lightning-fast precision. This is a non-smoker vehicle with no pet hair or lingering odors, offering a pure and engaging driving experience for its next owner.",
